        _row(d, "A water district federated a second ArcGIS Server for raster analytics. Image services publish, but creating hosted web layers still fails validation though a hosting server is assigned. Before blaming the raster site, what should you verify?", "That the hosting server path, data store registration, and publishing account can satisfy hosted layer workflows—not only federated raster capability.", "Unregister the hosting server.", "Install Portal on the raster machine.", "Disable HTTPS on the raster site."),
        _row(d, "A defense contractor’s SAML IdP sits in a DMZ. Classified workstations cannot reach the IdP’s external metadata URL; lab users can. Logins fail on classified machines. What is the core issue?", "IdP endpoints and metadata must be reachable from every required client network; use internal IdP aliases or split metadata—not a single external-only discovery path.", "Delete SAML and use anonymous access.", "Lower TLS to 1.0 for classified subnets.", "Disable Portal firewall rules entirely."),
        _row(d, "Notebook Server jobs that arcpy.read file shares fail with path not found, while the same UNC works in Pro on an analyst desktop. Interactive notebook test on Server succeeds when data is copied local. What should you check first?", "The Notebook Server run-as account has OS permissions and stable UNC resolution to registered paths—not the analyst’s interactive profile.", "Reinstall Notebook on the analyst PC.", "Disable UNC and use C:\\\\users paths on the server.", "Delete the relational data store."),
        _row(d, "GeoEvent writes to hosted feature services. After a DR exercise the geodatabase moved subnets; feeds show ‘connected’ but counts flatline. Services start. What should you reconcile?", "Database connectivity, registration, and firewall paths from GeoEvent/Server to the DB at its new address—including service account reachability.", "Reinstall GeoEvent without testing connections.", "Disable feature services and use CSV exports only.", "Increase tile cache size on Portal."),
        _row(d, "A multi-machine Server site uses a load-balanced Web Adaptor. One node was rebuilt with a new hostname and rejoined without Esri’s documented join procedure. The site is inconsistent. Best next step?", "Remove the misjoined machine cleanly and rejoin per Esri multi-machine guidance so config store and cluster state stay coherent.", "Copy config folders between random servers.", "Run two sites with one config store path.", "Ignore hostname changes."),
        _row(d, "Hosted scene layer caches stall at high LODs; hosting machine disks show free space and relational store is green. What should you inspect next?", "Tile cache / scene cache data store health, permissions, and capacity for deep pyramids—not only OS free space on C:.", "Delete the scene service.", "Move Portal to another domain.", "Set all map services to a single instance."),
