        _row(d, "PII map layers require user attribution in audit logs. IWA is enabled on the Web Adaptor, yet public kiosk maps hit anonymous paths. Auditors see only anonymous access. What explains missing user identity?", "Anonymous or public app flows do not carry IWA user context; separate authenticated endpoints or app design is needed for per-user auditing.", "Enable anonymous IWA simultaneously for all URLs.", "Delete Web Adaptor logging.", "Turn off HTTPS for kiosk browsers."),
        _row(d, "A reverse proxy strips WebSocket upgrade headers. Portal home loads but hosted feature layer editing and some admin pages fail intermittently. What should be corrected?", "Proxy rules for WebSockets, long polling, timeouts, and Host forwarding per Esri reverse-proxy documentation.", "Disable editing in Portal org settings.", "Open port 6080 to the internet.", "Delete hosted layers."),
        _row(d, "Architects want vector tiles and editable features from the same authoritative data. What must be explicit in the design?", "Which workflows use hosting/relational store versus enterprise GDB services, tile generation cadence, and editing paths—not assuming one mechanism covers all.", "Vector tiles automatically replace feature services.", "Hosted layers cannot coexist with tiles.", "Disable editing for all vector layers."),
        _row(d, "A read-only warehouse GDB is registered; leadership now wants hosted editing against the same warehouse without a staging GDB. What tension should you surface?", "Hosted editing patterns, performance, and transactional behavior differ from direct enterprise publishing; plan schema, branching, and store roles deliberately.", "Enable editing without DBA review.", "Copy the warehouse to file geodatabase weekly.", "Merge warehouses into Portal content dir."),
        _row(d, "After a merger, the portal public URL changed. Field apps still embed the old hostname in saved web maps. DNS points to the new name. What still breaks OAuth clients?", "Client-stored URLs, OAuth redirect registrations, and organization links must be updated to the canonical portal name—DNS alone does not rewrite app data.", "Delete all items.", "Disable OAuth for mobile.", "Share primary admin password for scripts."),
        _row(d, "A synchronous flood model GP service times out under load while the portal UI stays responsive. Leadership blames Portal. What is the best isolation step?", "Measure GP service instances, tool I/O, and data paths; scale and tune the GP service—not assume Portal is the bottleneck.", "Add Portal machines only.", "Set GP to asynchronous without testing.", "Disable all hosted layers."),
        _row(d, "FIPS-only TLS is enforced; legacy rugged tablets cannot handshake with the Web Adaptor. What process should security and GIS follow?", "Test cipher suites against all required clients and negotiate a supported baseline—not maximum hardening without device inventory.", "Disable TLS on internal VLANs.", "Exempt GIS from all crypto policy.", "Use HTTP for tablets only."),
